text: "Find the Way" is the 9th single by Mika Nakashima. It peaked on the Oricon weekly charts at #4 and sold roughly 124,489 copies. 'Find the Way' was used as the third ending theme for the anime series 'Mobile Suit Gundam SEED.' ==Track listing== # Find the Way # Find the Way (Instrumental) # Seppun (接吻;Kiss) (At-tica Remix) # Find the Way (Jamaals Manatee Mix by the Orb) ==References== Category:2003 singles Category:Mika Nakashima songs Category:Songs written by Mika Nakashima
title: Find the Way
